OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FVolunteer police officers  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto be armed with Taser stun
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fguns                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Volunteer police officers in England   
OL,6, and Wales will be authorised to use    
OL,7, Tasers, the home secretary is to       
OL,8, announce.                              
OL,10,FPriti Patel will say in a speech to    
OL,11,Fpolice that special constables should  
OL,12,Fbe able to use the electric stun guns  
OL,13,Fif they complete the specific training.
OL,15,FThe Home Office said it would ensure   
OL,16,Fthey are not "at a disadvantage" when  
OL,17,Ffacing attackers.                      
OL,19,FBut Amnesty International called it a  
OL,20,F"dangerous expansion" in their use.    
